tmiranda.mus
Class MultiFavorite

java.lang.Object
  tmiranda.mus.MultiObject
      tmiranda.mus.MultiFavorite

public class MultiFavorite
extends MultiObject

Class that implements the SageTV FavoriteAPI for multiple users. Unless noted otherwise the methods behave in the same way as the Sage core APIs.

initializeUser

@Deprecated
public void initializeUser()

Adds the current User to the Favorite database. This method is depreciated, addFavorite should be used instead.

clearUserFromFlags

@Deprecated
public void clearUserFromFlags()
Deprecated. 

Removes the current User from the Favorites database. Does NOT change remove the underlying Sage Favorite even if the User being removed is the last User. This method is depreciated, removeFavorite should be used instead.
